-- Vestas Names Anders Runevad CEO as Ditlev Engel Leaves
-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 2013-08-21T06:30:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-21/vestas-names-anders-runevad-ceo-as-ditlev-engel-leaves.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S (VWS)  named Anders
Runevad as chief executive officer and group president,
succeeding Ditlev Engel after the Danish wind turbine maker
posted two successive years of losses.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Morales in London at 
